name: Personalized Vacation Frame
description:
Let Us Put Your Vacation Location and Date on this frame to treasure forever.  Made from engineered wood offering an extremely tight and smooth surface. Perfect for vacations, honeymoons, anniversaries or any of your favorite memories.

The photo opening is 4"X6" and the frame dimension is 10"X12".
Fade Resistant! Made in the USA.

Please add your personalization details in the "notes to seller" field at checkout.

name: Personalized Canvas A Toast to Tuscany
description: Framed art with your name on it. We'll customize a canvas just for you or a unique gift for someone special. Simply provide the necessary information unique to each image. We will create a one-of-a-kind canvas, mount and frame it. Image size, 18" x 9". Framed size, 22" x 13" with 2" black-finished moulding. Ready to hang.    Please specify date and 2 first names in preferred order, last name, city and state in the "notes to seller" field at checkout.
